commit.message:
Add gtktoolbutton and gtk-widget-get-name

From Stephen Lewis https://sourceforge.net/p/gauche/mailman/gauche-devel/?viewmonth=202203
Change tarball name to be consistent with the package name

Cosmetic cleanup

- Remove trailing whitespaces
- Remove RCS ID (finally!)

Fix deprecated glib calls

NB: g_type_init() is now done automatically and no longer needed
to call it explicitly.

Temporarily disable GC tests

Debugging code seems to prevent collection of the objects in a
desired timing.
Update obsoleted Gauche API calls to new ones.

Merge pull request #6 from tsutomu-hiroshima/original-readme

Enable some features ignored by genstub
